{"tid":1844230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【瑪嘉烈醫院嘅最新情況】","createTime":"2020-01-26T14:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T07:35:13.000Z","uid":53003,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"778edafccdb3294f1a9fca0f0b5fcbdcb88f4f89","tid":1844230,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"你知道嗎？全港只有一個傳染病中心。<br />\n<br />\n所有武漢肺炎確診個案都係送往同一個地方&mdash;&mdash;瑪嘉烈醫院嘅S座，裡面有7個isolation ward&mdash;s8-12, s14-15，每個ward有12個cubicle(s8只有10個)，屈指一算，總共只夠接收82個patient。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100004714003899/posts/1448677975299322?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100004714003899%2Fposts%2F1448677975299322%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=26cb2de2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100004714003899/posts/1448677975299322?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"fa1d862a8f562bb92f54485ef62182c6d9d42b32","tid":1844230,"uid":104803,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:14:43.000Z","msg":"82個WTF"},{"pid":"398b626ff0d35c572a9b25cb16997dae87aad4d9","tid":1844230,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15d43de1a4788b42e785198ac72b28427cd4dc8e","tid":1844230,"uid":53003,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">得82個咋！</span>"},{"pid":"9429b3f993f4daba8f1091e168a02749ead0d6f0","tid":1844230,"uid":258731,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:16:28.000Z","msg":"【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"894ee835eca8f066ed7fdcbb2fad2aabf2d878d4","tid":1844230,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3471dfc6db041b15ed017740c5a9ac49e1dcbf5b","tid":1844230,"uid":174060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ad9424072fcb8aa6f72834159ee9199efa9edb40","tid":1844230,"uid":103050,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"黎多80個武漢人就gg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1dc5a27586a6db0b77bd0bf96ee91342e3509cf","tid":1844230,"uid":5725,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"其實我諗全港既隔離病房應該唔多， 如果多人感染真係玩撚完<br />\n一定大爆發"},{"pid":"77f9cea4b6dc356d9d9b6ff74203d30193bb49b8","tid":1844230,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6fd005f9ebeb7da00f4b0a9d354934a79c2578d","tid":1844230,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"